title: Shane's World - California Dreamin'
description: Casey wanted to get to know her new home state, so she grabbed some friends and headed out to see what Cali has to offer. Casey, Paulina and Jack headed out for some fun in the sun and a naughty threesome in Catalina. Devon shows Casey Malibu AND a good time. Then she hops on a plane to Napa for her first wine tasting f=with friends Aubrey and Criss. Next to San Francisco for some chowder and sightseeing with Reena and Dane. Back home Casey shows Charles why she still loves LA the most! Check out what Cali and Casey have to offer you! San Francisco, Catalina, Napa & More! Casey LOVES Cali!
